/>\n<br />\n一次過滿足香港人三個願望 大家又唔洗內鬥同再嘈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攪炒巴團隊請入!!! 不才有拙計 「關於機場運動」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463142</a>"},{"pid":"390bf5979a68ca6cc4b94b5ba73ebaed1fa94650","tid":1465952,"uid":260088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c92a347b424b26dac3e983287a1bbf86e33b4772","tid":1465952,"uid":72590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3149848e6bbd8c7d8c110ca132ff6ec32368712","tid":1465952,"uid":244418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"421aa7ff965c286eb62270bfc502918a9c5c4575","tid":1465952,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:36.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300d57815155cba7b29d10c5a428b4fef4cdcd58","tid":1465952,"uid":72590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d80e2587a450b744d3291986fe59540695c7380","tid":1465952,"uid":83523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:13.000Z","msg":"其實大家今次只係衝動左d遮<br />\n<br />\n未去到恆常化<br />\n<br />\n無咁易逆轉民意既<br />\n<br />\n係有少少失左儀態<br />\n<br />\n今晚就當係一時衝動，我唸支持我地既人都會理解。<br />\n<br />\n最重要唔好學政府死不悔改既態度<br />\n<br />\n俗語有云：有錯就要認，打就要企定。<br />\n<br />\n現在個勢都仲係我地度既<br />\n<br />\n睇睇聽日國際傳媒點評價今次事件<br />\n<br />\n我地再唸對策。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係想做多d既，可以向機場舉牌道歉，比外國傳媒睇。<br />\n<br />\n至於鬼方面，我地冷處理先<br />\n<br />\n因為防不勝防，佢地在暗<br />\n<br />\n最重要和理非就一齊和理非<br />\n<br />\n果d所謂鬼，到佢地見成朝無人起哄。<br />\n<br />\n佢地一定露出馬腳按奈唔住會突然發癲。<br />\n<br />\n千祈咪搞佢，你同佢鬥理論係只會令自己情緒失控。<br />\n<br />\n就好易中招。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會都開始將制裁措施一個一個擺出黎等復會就通過。<br />\n<br />\n我地需要沉默應戰"},{"pid":"3c269b1e8a3677d5eae8e41eb0d6e4ce20c03d96","tid":1465952,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"黎互推<br />\n［文宣方向／準備］狗改不了吃屎，今晚機場又係福建幫ｘ黑狗ｘ公安，破壞機場和理非！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDKHuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDKHuS</a>"},{"pid":"d1c5bfed7ca53d343361e14f219a1f515d4b77c6","tid":1465952,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcb717c34c9b45e1ed69bac1e15abb2e4261a38b","tid":1465952,"uid":269967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:47.000Z","msg":"頭破血流<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/quKU8Lq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FquKU8Lq.jpg&h=ee65e835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/503084439752305/posts/2433239213403475/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F503084439752305%2Fposts%2F2433239213403475%2F&d=3XxoN59xZ6GKXDea4epuE0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=dc0b70f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/503084439752305/posts/2433239213403475/</a>"},{"pid":"e0727e6d67871a14d9c7b05b39ca0542b1e3ea31","tid":1465952,"uid":72590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"上到熱門我停手了，希望真係有人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305259cd8aafc56da4289bfd60db09ff9779aaa3","tid":1465952,"uid":114346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13